User Story

Maria is born and raised in Dallas, Texas who moved to San Francisco with her family 2 years ago.  She has a vibrant personality and has an active lifestyle.  She likes hanging out with friends, travelling, running, swimming.  She also volunteers in an animal shelter every saturday to care for neglected pets.  She is currently a grade 12 student and has not decided which career path to take which is best suitable for her lifestyle.  Just like most of millenials, having a balanced life is a priority, but not compromising the opportunity to earn well for a comfortable lifestyle.  Life is short.  You only life once. Carpe Diem! 

Use Case

(1)  What industry/job has a good working hours with a good pay, so that she can maintain her work-life balance. 

